e old 2.x/3.x API: `PooledBoltConnectionProvider`, `RoutingContext`, and `DatabaseNameUtil` are not present for this artifact version. Instantiate `PooledBoltConnectionSource` directly and provide small hand-written test fakes/stubs for `BoltConnectionProvider`, `BoltConnection`, `AuthTokenManager`, `SecurityPlanSupplier`, `MetricsListener`, and `LoggingProvider`. Use completed `CompletionStage` values and `NotificationConfig.defaultConfig()` where suitable. The pooled artifact wraps an upstream provider and does not itself require a live Neo4j server, Netty transport, Docker image, system property, or environment variable for unit-level coverage.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The library README says this module is intended for Neo4j drivers/internal consumers and gives no API guarantees, so stale 3.0 tests are likely to fail against 4.0 due to breaking API changes.\",\n    \"Official upstream tests use Mockito, but adding Mockito is not required for meaningful coverage and may introduce unnecessary native-image metadata surface; hand-written fakes are safer.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0d69f7780b098d0e016a3ed8113b908197988f46255e193840\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3202, "output": 676, "cacheRead": 45056, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48934, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782503434106, "responseId": "resp_0d69f7780b098d0e016a3ed80aaa7881979cb002b825439a4a"}}
